A scrapper base on PhantomJS.
A compiled version of PhantomJS (linux 64bit) is included.

Usage (for the moment):
 ./lib/bin/phantomjs-impl/phantomjs-linux-64/bin/phantomjs ./lib/js/main.js http://example.com

Result:
