Notes:
 * The scrapper tries to  simulate *ALL* JavaScript click events on the page
 * The scrapper send 1000 clicks to random locations on the page just in case
 * The timeouts are tunable, as as well as the whole process, by editing "./lib/js/main.js"
 * The perl scripts included currently don't work.

